# {BRAND_NAME} — Workspace Context

{ONE_LINER}

This file is the entry point for every Claude Code session in this directory. It tells Claude where to find specific business context for specific kinds of work.

## When to read which file

| Task | Read these |
|---|---|
| Writing ad copy | `context/voice.md`, `context/positioning.md`, `context/audience.md` |
| Social media post | `context/voice.md`, `context/audience.md`, `context/results.md` |
| Web copy / landing page | `context/voice.md`, `context/positioning.md`, `context/offers.md`, `context/results.md` |
| Strategy / business decisions | All 8 context files |
| Pricing / new offer design | `context/offers.md`, `context/results.md`, `context/audience.md` |
| Sales call talking points | `context/audience.md`, `context/results.md`, `context/offers.md` |
| Funnel design / customer journey | `context/funnel.md`, `context/audience.md`, `context/offers.md` |
| Brand voice questions | `context/voice.md` only |
| Competitor analysis | `context/positioning.md`, `context/audience.md`, `context/offers.md` |

